# pre-commit.blocked-files — list filenames that should never be committed
#
# Copy this file to .githooks/pre-commit.blocked-files and customise.
# The file is intentionally excluded from mac-setup tracking (.gitignore)
# because blocked filenames are machine-local preferences.
#
# Format:
#   - One entry per line
#   - Lines starting with # are comments
#   - Blank lines are ignored
#   - Entries are matched as fixed strings against staged file paths (grep -F)
#     so "work-log.md" matches any path ending in work-log.md
#
# Example entries:
work-log.md
# .env.local
# secrets.json
